Revision history for Tickit-Widget-Statusbar

0.006     2024-02-16 05:19:23+08:00 Asia/Singapore
    [Bugs fixed]

    - latest Tickit::Widget and Tickit::Style require Object::Pad-compatible classes

0.005     2020-09-19 14:34:56+08:00 Asia/Kuala_Lumpur
    No new features.

    Bugs fixed:

    - Proc::CPUUsage fails tests, switching to BSD::Resource instead
    - Window handling changes in recent Tickit versions were causing segfaults,
    seems to be caused by creating new windows instead of changing geometry

0.004     2015-01-24 08:58:54+00:00 Europe/London
	No new features.

	Bugs fixed:
	* Status is set correctly on instantiation

0.003     2014-08-20 20:59:21+01:00 Europe/London
	New features:
	* ->update_status now accepts a String::Tagged object

0.002     2014-08-16 03:30:15+01:00 Europe/London
	Bugs fixed:
	* Redraw after reshape

	Dependency fixes:
	* Tickit::Widget, add in Tickit::Widget::Progressbar as well

0.001     2013-09-01 03:56:00 Europe/London
	Initial CPAN release
